Q: How to update selected items?
A: Double click selected item to enable update form. Double is not supported in supplier & purchase page. (Button Support Only)
Q: How to add item(s)/Supplier/Purchase?
A: Go to desired page and click new button.
Q: What is access level?
A: It determines privilege acces of the user to the software. (eg. Admin level can access all system functions while user has only limited actions.)
Q: Can User level access logs?
A: No, only Admin level can access logs and export/print functions.
